name: CircularFifoQueue_removeTest
description: Unit tests for the remove functionality of the CircularFifoQueue class.

test_cases.name: testRemoveSuccess
test_cases.description: Tests the successful removal of an element from the queue.

test_cases.name: testRemoveFromEmptyQueue
test_cases.description: Tests the removal of an element from an empty queue, expecting a NoSuchElementException.

test_cases.name: testRemoveWithWrapAround
test_cases.description: Tests the removal of an element from the queue after it has wrapped around.

test_cases.name: testRemoveAllElements
test_cases.description: Tests the removal of all elements from the queue.

test_cases.name: testRemoveAfterClear
test_cases.description: Tests the removal of an element from the queue after it has been cleared, expecting a NoSuchElementException.
